  "summary": "Bright Data toolkit enables scalable search, crawl, and scraping without getting blocked. It provides programmatic access to search engine queries, page-to-markdown conversion, and structured data feeds across many sites and content types.\n\n**Capabilities**\n- High-throughput, proxy-backed scraping with anti-blocking, rotation, and anonymity.\n- Query and normalize search engine results into consumable Markdown or structured outputs.\n- Extract structured entities, reviews, listings, profiles and other site-specific data with pagination and batching.\n- Flexible output formats (Markdown, JSON) and parameterized feeds for filters, locales, and result counts.\n\n**Secrets**\nUses two secret types: API key and zone/token. Examples: BRIGHTDATA_API_KEY (your service key, e.g. BRIGHTDATA_API_KEY=sk_live_...), BRIGHTDATA_ZONE (proxy/zone identifier, e.g. BRIGHTDATA_ZONE=my_zone_id)."
